[DISTANT SIRENS WAILING]

28:38.804 --> 28:40.038
Come up.

28:41.973 --> 28:43.909
- Who's the guy?
- I don't know, man.

28:43.975 --> 28:45.343
[DOOR BUZZES]

28:45.477 --> 28:46.843
MAN: You ever seen that guy?

28:46.845 --> 28:48.146
DEALER: No, man.

28:50.549 --> 28:51.883
