28:57.657 --> 29:00.357
So, how did it go?

29:00.359 --> 29:01.593
JULIETTE: Fine.

29:04.062 --> 29:05.397
Who is he?

29:06.199 --> 29:07.633
He's okay, don't worry.

29:08.601 --> 29:10.703
