29:28.456 --> 29:29.823
Have fun.

29:42.871 --> 29:44.239
You want a drink?

29:45.707 --> 29:46.907
JACK: Whiskey?

29:47.441 --> 29:48.741
I haven't got any.

29:48.743 --> 29:51.311
- Tea?
- Yeah, tea's fine.

29:56.451 --> 29:57.886
[STOVE IGNITING]

30:04.125 --> 30:05.560
[WATER RUNNING]

30:14.937 --> 30:16.337
[KNOCKS ON FISH TANK]

30:22.979 --> 30:24.379
Do you mind if I sit?

30:29.218 --> 30:30.486
It's okay.

30:31.654 --> 30:33.389
[KETTLE WHISTLING]

30:46.603 --> 30:47.804
Thanks.

31:00.785 --> 31:02.320
[LIGHTER CLICKS]

31:05.790 --> 31:07.124
[LIGHTER CLATTERING]

31:12.229 --> 31:13.731
I like your plants.

31:19.837 --> 31:21.672
That's called an air plant.

31:22.574 --> 31:25.610
JACK: Yeah, they grow
without sun or water.

31:26.411 --> 31:28.046
No roots, huh?

31:29.380 --> 31:30.548
May I?

31:41.460 --> 31:42.861
[COUGHS]

31:43.562 --> 31:44.763
It's strong.

31:54.440 --> 31:56.540
Last time, you didn't
give me your number,

31:56.542 --> 31:58.776
so when I saw you in
the bar, I thought...

31:58.778 --> 32:00.412
Why not follow her home?

32:20.567 --> 32:22.903
What exactly is
it that you want?

32:24.905 --> 32:27.141
I just wanted
to see you again.

32:29.910 --> 32:31.477
Well, there you go.

32:35.083 --> 32:36.418
This is me.

32:38.920 --> 32:40.188
So what?

32:41.422 --> 32:43.124
I'm not here to judge.

32:43.457 --> 32:44.959
JULIETTE:
You're not here to judge?

32:45.593 --> 32:46.993
Who the fuck
do you think you are

32:46.995 --> 32:48.662
to follow me home and say that?

32:49.798 --> 32:51.833
You're not here
to judge what exactly?

32:52.834 --> 32:54.269
This shitty apartment?

32:54.936 --> 32:56.503
The guy at the door?

32:57.806 --> 32:59.074
Me?

33:02.145 --> 33:04.479
- I can help you if you want.
- Help?

33:05.580 --> 33:07.983
You think I want
your fucking help?

33:09.317 --> 33:11.954
I don't want your charity.
Get out.

33:13.455 --> 33:14.824
Come on, get out.

33:15.024 --> 33:16.624
- JACK: Wait, I...
- I asked you to leave.

33:16.626 --> 33:17.827
Get out!

33:20.063 --> 33:21.897
I don't fucking want you here!

33:23.199 --> 33:26.500
Listen, maybe following
you was a bad idea, okay?

33:26.502 --> 33:27.968
JULIETTE: Or maybe
you wanna stay.

33:27.970 --> 33:29.171
Is that it?

33:31.207 --> 33:32.675
Is that what you want?

33:33.143 --> 33:34.643
JACK: Don't do that.

33:37.648 --> 33:40.549
[♪♪♪♪♪]

33:43.554 --> 33:45.822
Don't you wanna
keep the party going?

33:46.890 --> 33:48.558
Why are you leaving?

34:02.539 --> 34:03.975
[NEEDLE CLATTERING]

34:25.864 --> 34:27.299
[EXHALES]

34:44.984 --> 34:46.351
[RADIO STATIC]

34:46.452 --> 34:48.786
This is Juliette, I'm injured.
I need help.

34:49.121 --> 34:51.056
[RADIO STATIC]

34:54.527 --> 34:55.893
Someone answer me.

34:55.896 --> 34:57.629
[RADIO STATIC]

34:57.631 --> 35:00.400
- Answer me, goddamn it.
- [RADIO STATIC]

35:00.934 --> 35:02.534
Answer me!

35:02.536 --> 35:04.204
[RADIO STATIC]

35:04.304 --> 35:05.937
[CREATURE GROWLING]

35:05.939 --> 35:09.943
- [GASPS]
- [♪♪♪♪♪]

35:12.113 --> 35:16.049
[CREATURE GROWLING, SNARLING]

35:17.717 --> 35:19.220
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

35:21.656 --> 35:24.024
[GRUNTS]

35:25.193 --> 35:28.295
- [CREATURE SNARLING]
- [GRUNTS]

35:31.332 --> 35:35.604
[CREATURE GROWLING, SNARLING]

35:37.772 --> 35:39.773
[CREATURE SNIFFING]

35:52.955 --> 35:54.521
HARRY: [OVER RADIO]
<i>Juliette, do you copy?</i>

35:54.523 --> 35:56.423
<i>Juliette, Juliette,
are you the...</i>

35:56.425 --> 35:57.627
[TURNS RADIO OFF]

36:05.367 --> 36:08.371
[WIND HOWLING]

36:13.109 --> 36:15.478
[CREATURE GROWLING, SNARLING]

36:15.979 --> 36:17.545
HARRY: [OVER RADIO]
<i>Juliette, are you there?</i>

36:17.547 --> 36:18.613
<i>Do you copy?</i>

36:18.615 --> 36:20.816
<i>Damn it, Juliette, answer me!</i>

36:21.451 --> 36:22.785
<i>Where are you?</i>

36:23.320 --> 36:24.552
[CREATURE GROWLING, SQUEALING]

36:24.554 --> 36:25.853
<i>Look, if you can hear me,</i>

36:25.855 --> 36:28.090
<i>you have to do
exactly what I say,</i>

36:28.092 --> 36:29.926
<i>so we can find you.</i>

36:30.027 --> 36:31.761
<i>Now, listen up, Juliette.</i>

36:32.395 --> 36:34.064
<i>You've gotta go in the back.</i>

36:34.697 --> 36:36.400
- <i>There's a...</i>
- [RADIO SMASHES]

36:40.204 --> 36:42.739
[CREATURE BREATHING, SNARLING]

36:48.679 --> 36:51.348
[METAL CREAKING]

36:51.882 --> 36:55.919
[DISTANT CREATURE ROARING]

36:59.991 --> 37:01.526
