37:34.460 --> 37:36.829
[SHELLS CLATTERING]

37:46.672 --> 37:48.408
[FIRE CRACKLING]

37:59.454 --> 38:00.954
[DOORBELL RINGING]

38:09.963 --> 38:11.399
[ELEVATOR DINGS]

38:12.599 --> 38:16.470
[♪♪♪♪♪]

39:17.801 --> 39:19.902
[SEAGULLS CRYING]

39:25.008 --> 39:26.377
JULIETTE: Hey.

39:27.044 --> 39:28.379
Hey.

39:30.948 --> 39:33.015
JULIETTE: Thanks
for last night.

39:34.785 --> 39:36.854
Come and try to eat something.

39:47.466 --> 39:49.066
Is it bad?

39:49.633 --> 39:51.401
No, it's not bad.

39:51.403 --> 39:52.871
I'm just not hungry.

39:55.974 --> 39:58.276
Do you wanna talk
about what happened?

40:01.379 --> 40:03.014
Do you wanna talk at all?

40:03.715 --> 40:05.350
What do you wanna talk about?

40:05.417 --> 40:06.584
JACK: I don't know.

40:07.619 --> 40:09.755
Maybe about my bad
cooking skills.

40:10.356 --> 40:12.055
I told you, it's not bad.

40:12.057 --> 40:15.360
Great, then I won't fire
the guy who cooked it for us.

40:15.595 --> 40:16.796
[JACK CHUCKLES]

40:22.201 --> 40:26.539
You know, when I arrived
here, when my parents died,

40:27.106 --> 40:29.373
I really struggled
with all this.

40:29.375 --> 40:30.743
With all this?

40:31.310 --> 40:34.412
Everything, I mean,
I felt like a fish

40:34.414 --> 40:35.816
in an aquarium.

40:36.782 --> 40:39.586
- It's a nice aquarium.
- JACK: Yeah, but it wasn't me.

40:40.153 --> 40:42.121
I had to get used to it.

40:46.593 --> 40:50.130
What I'm trying to say
is you could do the same.

40:51.431 --> 40:52.699
Maybe.

40:56.470 --> 40:58.538
Do you mind if I take a
walk around the block?

41:00.174 --> 41:01.508
You need a fix.

41:04.345 --> 41:06.146
Just be honest, say it.

41:07.582 --> 41:08.982
Where are you going?

41:18.927 --> 41:20.261
[JACK SIGHS]

41:21.996 --> 41:23.462
Open this fucking door.

41:23.464 --> 41:24.699
JACK: No.

41:25.434 --> 41:27.703
- What do you mean, "no"?
- JACK: You're staying here.

41:28.937 --> 41:30.672
No, I'm fucking not.

41:31.706 --> 41:33.607
JACK: I won't let
you go, not this time.

41:33.609 --> 41:35.007
JULIETTE: You
can't fucking do this.

41:35.009 --> 41:36.076
[GRUNTS]

41:36.078 --> 41:37.910
I'm not your little experiment.

41:37.912 --> 41:39.680
Look, I know you're gonna
hate me for doing this,

41:39.682 --> 41:41.081
but you're gonna stay,

41:41.083 --> 41:43.517
as long as it takes me
to get you off that shit.

41:43.519 --> 41:45.921
You have no right to do this.

41:46.855 --> 41:49.324
[SCREAMS]

41:50.092 --> 41:51.225
Help!
[SCREAMS]

41:51.227 --> 41:52.694
You can scream
as much as you like.

41:52.696 --> 41:53.927
I own the whole floor.

41:53.929 --> 41:55.330
Scream.

42:00.437 --> 42:02.070
[OBJECTS CLATTERING]

42:02.072 --> 42:04.741
Oh, that's it, go
ahead, break everything.

42:04.908 --> 42:07.242
I don't care.
That's it, yeah.

42:07.244 --> 42:08.810
[OBJECTS SMASHING]

42:08.812 --> 42:10.213
Come on, do it.

42:10.480 --> 42:12.549
Give me what you got, come on.

42:13.483 --> 42:15.383
- [GLASS SMASHING]
- Enough now, that's it.

42:15.385 --> 42:16.884
- That's it.
- JULIETTE: Get the fuck a...

42:16.886 --> 42:18.687
- Get the fuck away from me!
- Juliette, stop that.

42:18.689 --> 42:20.656
- JACK: Stop that.
- JULIETTE: Get the fuck off me!

42:20.658 --> 42:23.659
- Get the fuck off!
- JACK: Stop that now, enough!

42:23.661 --> 42:26.695
Enough, enough,
stop it, calm down.

42:26.697 --> 42:28.699
- Calm down.
- [JULIETTE CRIES]

42:29.333 --> 42:32.703
Shh, shh, it's okay.

42:33.004 --> 42:37.207
[♪♪♪♪♪]

42:50.255 --> 42:52.724
[WIND HOWLING]

42:56.228 --> 42:57.662
[CLICKS]

43:08.240 --> 43:12.110
[♪♪♪♪♪]

43:14.913 --> 43:16.114
[GRUNTS]

43:27.060 --> 43:28.494
[GRUNTS]

43:37.270 --> 43:38.772
[GRUNTS]

44:02.896 --> 44:05.066
- [RUNNING FOOTSTEPS]
- [COCKS GUN]

44:34.296 --> 44:35.497
[GRUNTS]

44:59.021 --> 45:01.891
- [CREATURE ROARS]
- [GUNSHOT]

45:02.092 --> 45:03.958
[♪♪♪♪♪]

45:03.960 --> 45:06.129
[CREATURE ROARING]

45:10.701 --> 45:11.634
[GUN COCKS]

45:11.636 --> 45:14.205
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

45:23.046 --> 45:26.417
[♪♪♪♪♪]

45:31.088 --> 45:32.221
[SCREAMS]

45:32.223 --> 45:33.758
[CREATURE ROARS]

45:39.297 --> 45:41.432
- [SCREAMS]
- [CREATURE GROWLS]

45:44.770 --> 45:46.605
[ENGINE STARTS]

45:49.741 --> 45:51.977
- [ENGINE REVVING]
- [CREATURE SCREAMS]

45:52.678 --> 45:53.979
[GUN COCKS]

46:00.986 --> 46:02.487
[RUNNING FOOTSTEPS]

46:04.757 --> 46:06.323
- [RUNNING FOOTSTEPS]
- [GUNSHOTS]

46:06.325 --> 46:08.027
[SCREAMS]

46:18.104 --> 46:19.303
[CREATURE GRUNTING]

46:19.305 --> 46:20.740
- [SCREAMS]
- [GUNSHOT]

46:20.907 --> 46:23.074
[HIGH-PITCHED RINGING]

46:23.076 --> 46:25.078
[MUFFLED CRYING AND PANTING]

46:30.751 --> 46:33.821
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

46:40.594 --> 46:41.995
[GRUNTS]

46:59.814 --> 47:00.982
[WHISPERING]
No.

47:01.416 --> 47:02.917
[FLASK CLATTERING]

47:07.556 --> 47:08.990
Mm.

47:11.426 --> 47:12.893
JACK: They're almost done.

47:12.895 --> 47:14.327
The rest goes
in the garage, guys.

47:14.329 --> 47:15.530
Thanks.

47:16.531 --> 47:17.866
Thank you.

47:22.972 --> 47:24.340
Hey, princess.

47:25.173 --> 47:26.976
- JULIETTE: Mm-hmm?
- You okay?

47:29.378 --> 47:31.614
Surprises always make
me a little nervous.

47:31.747 --> 47:34.683
[♪♪♪♪♪]

47:36.419 --> 47:37.686
You know what?

47:38.387 --> 47:41.757
My mother used to do
something to make me smile.

47:42.558 --> 47:44.060
She used to do this.

47:46.095 --> 47:47.529
[LAUGHS]

47:47.931 --> 47:50.566
You see? It works.
[CHUCKLES]

47:53.470 --> 47:55.171
Can we go in now?

47:55.439 --> 47:57.406
Yeah, let me show you.

48:15.927 --> 48:18.296
Hey, come.

48:20.365 --> 48:21.933
Ta-da!

48:22.367 --> 48:23.733
Huh.

48:23.735 --> 48:26.435
So then, we could move
the sofa there, you know?

48:26.437 --> 48:28.407
Or put some plants.

48:28.906 --> 48:30.541
I've got a few ideas.

48:31.110 --> 48:32.576
What about you?

48:32.710 --> 48:34.779
What do you mean
what about me?

48:34.980 --> 48:36.545
Where are we gonna put you?

48:36.547 --> 48:38.417
You can put me
wherever you like.

48:38.449 --> 48:40.249
[LAUGHS]
Are you sure about that?

48:40.251 --> 48:41.719
Yeah.

48:42.054 --> 48:43.285
Where do you wanna put me?

48:43.287 --> 48:44.788
Uh, a little further.

48:44.790 --> 48:47.224
Watch out, watch out.
Yeah, not there.

48:47.226 --> 48:48.892
More this way, this way.

48:48.894 --> 48:50.262
Stop.

48:50.396 --> 48:52.429
- What do we think?
- That's where I belong.

48:52.431 --> 48:54.464
- Yeah, it's a good place for you.
- Yeah? Okay.

48:54.466 --> 48:57.002
JULIETTE: Uh, I might have
to change a couple things.

48:57.971 --> 48:59.538
Come on.
[LAUGHS]

49:00.639 --> 49:01.975
Seriously?

49:02.374 --> 49:04.277
Okay, but you're missing
something.

49:04.811 --> 49:06.545
[JACK CHUCKLES]

49:07.647 --> 49:10.515
Oh, God.
Okay.

49:11.718 --> 49:13.386
- Right there.
- JACK: All right.

49:14.187 --> 49:17.288
But I don't know if I want you
in the living room...

49:17.290 --> 49:19.891
[LAUGHS]
...or the bedroom.

49:19.893 --> 49:21.492
JACK: Then let's have
a look upstairs.

49:21.494 --> 49:23.330
- Stop with that game. Come.
- [JULIETTE GIGGLES]

49:29.502 --> 49:32.339
Okay, this is
the master bedroom.

49:32.540 --> 49:34.208
JULIETTE: It's beautiful.

49:34.542 --> 49:36.642
Hold on, princess,
you haven't seen the view

49:36.644 --> 49:38.045
from the kid's room yet.

49:39.480 --> 49:40.781
The what?

49:44.685 --> 49:46.819
What do you mean
"the kid's" bedroom.

49:46.821 --> 49:48.054
JACK: I don't know.
It could be.

49:48.056 --> 49:50.291
- Come here.
- You're kidding, right?

49:51.325 --> 49:52.659
Just have a look.

49:54.162 --> 49:55.829
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

49:56.230 --> 49:59.034
This is what a child would
wake up to every morning.

49:59.901 --> 50:03.036
So, you want us to have a baby
because of the nice view?

50:03.038 --> 50:06.908
No, just because a child
would be happy here.

50:07.609 --> 50:10.045
And we'd always be here
for him or her.

50:10.545 --> 50:11.745
You don't know that.

50:11.747 --> 50:13.446
Of course I don't, and so what.

50:13.448 --> 50:15.016
There's no way of knowing.

50:15.350 --> 50:16.551
That's life.

50:18.253 --> 50:20.087
And you know what,
we don't need to know.

50:20.089 --> 50:21.924
We just have to try
and make them happy.

50:22.892 --> 50:24.290
Maybe you could
make 'em happy,

50:24.292 --> 50:27.696
but... I don't know about me.

50:31.868 --> 50:33.470
Why are you so afraid?

50:33.703 --> 50:35.372
I'm not afraid.

50:37.573 --> 50:39.008
Do you love me at least?

50:40.543 --> 50:42.510
Do you actually have
any feelings for me?

50:42.512 --> 50:44.278
- You know.
- No, I don't.

50:44.280 --> 50:45.714
I need to hear it.

50:47.885 --> 50:49.052
Say it.

50:50.087 --> 50:51.955
For once in your life, say it.

50:54.591 --> 50:57.394
I have feelings for you.

50:58.229 --> 51:00.797
Say, I love you, motherfucker.

51:03.467 --> 51:04.766
Motherfucker.

51:04.768 --> 51:06.103
[LAUGHS]

51:32.131 --> 51:35.434
- [RADIO BEEPS]
- [RADIO STATIC]

51:35.768 --> 51:37.500
Harry, are you there?

51:37.502 --> 51:40.472
[RADIO STATIC]

51:41.307 --> 51:43.075
HARRY: <i>Shit, you scared us.</i>

51:43.442 --> 51:44.943
<i>What happened?</i>

51:45.110 --> 51:46.778
I had a bad car wreck.

51:47.012 --> 51:48.447
I broke my leg.

51:50.082 --> 51:51.283
I'm stuck.

51:52.319 --> 51:54.454
HARRY: <i>Do you know
where you are?</i>

51:56.022 --> 51:58.324
I think I'm near the main road,
heading north.

51:58.524 --> 52:00.560
One or two miles
from the gas station.

52:00.659 --> 52:01.860
HARRY: <i>Okay,
Juliette, you need to...</i>

52:01.862 --> 52:03.027
[RADIO STATIC]

52:03.029 --> 52:04.796
- <i>And get the...</i>
- [RADIO STATIC]

52:04.798 --> 52:06.497
<i>...activated.
Now we put some instructions...</i>

52:06.499 --> 52:08.334
- [RADIO STATIC]
- Can you repeat that?

52:09.236 --> 52:11.471
- HARRY: <i>...it all out for you...</i>
- [RADIO STATIC]

52:11.905 --> 52:14.072
<i>...the beacon.
Locator beacon.</i>

52:14.074 --> 52:16.042
[RADIO STATIC]

52:16.810 --> 52:18.379
The locator beacon?

52:19.347 --> 52:20.648
What do I do with it?

52:20.747 --> 52:24.582
- HARRY: <i>Hurry. Now, there is...</i>
- [RADIO STATIC]

52:24.584 --> 52:27.720
- <i>...you need to follow...</i>
- [RADIO STATIC]

52:28.856 --> 52:30.191
Harry?

52:32.392 --> 52:33.692
Harry, come in.

52:33.694 --> 52:36.897
[RADIO STATIC]

52:56.885 --> 52:58.186
[WHISPERING]
Okay.

53:02.524 --> 53:03.858
Hey.

53:08.697 --> 53:10.399
I have something to tell you.

53:10.599 --> 53:11.933
Oh, shit.

53:15.772 --> 53:17.139
JULIETTE: It's not easy.

53:18.775 --> 53:22.578
Juliette, you know you
can tell me anything.

53:29.786 --> 53:31.420
What do you like about me?

53:31.654 --> 53:33.788
JACK: Oh, baby, you
know what I like about you.

53:33.790 --> 53:35.690
I've told you a
million times already.

53:35.692 --> 53:37.728
Tell me again, please.

53:38.461 --> 53:39.762
Okay.

53:42.399 --> 53:43.766
I like...

53:49.139 --> 53:50.574
I like your legs.

53:51.208 --> 53:52.708
Come on, what else?

53:52.710 --> 53:53.909
[JACK CHUCKLES]

53:53.911 --> 53:57.548
Okay, I like how you
look when you're upset.

53:57.581 --> 53:59.584
You make a cute duck face.

53:59.917 --> 54:01.150
I do not.

54:01.152 --> 54:02.420
JACK: I swear you do,

54:02.653 --> 54:04.354
- something with your mouth.
- JULIETTE: Don't be a dick.

54:04.356 --> 54:05.822
